  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to analyze the peri-operative expression of pancreatic stone
      protein and pancreatitis-associated protein in surgical patients following major abdominal
      surgery by blood samples.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
